    {
      "id": "line-61",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Sleep is essential for our physical and mental health.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 9,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-62",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It allows our bodies to repair themselves and our brains to process information and consolidate memories.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 16,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-63",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Most adults need between 7 and 9 hours of sleep per night.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 12,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-64",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "However, many people do not get enough sleep.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 8,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-65",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "According to a recent survey, more than one-third of adults in the United States get less than 7 hours of sleep per night.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 24,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-66",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Lack of sleep can have serious consequences.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 7,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-67",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It can impair our judgment, reaction time, and memory.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 9,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-68",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It can also increase the risk of developing chronic diseases, such as diabetes, heart disease, and obesity.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 17,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-69",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "In addition, lack of sleep can lead to mood swings, irritability, and depression.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 13,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-70",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "To improve your sleep quality, you should establish a regular sleep schedule.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 12,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-71",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Go to bed and wake up at the same time every day, even on weekends.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 15,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-72",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "You should also create a relaxing bedtime routine, such as taking a warm bath, reading a book, or listening to soft music.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 22,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-73",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Avoid caffeine, alcohol, and nicotine before bedtime, as they can interfere with sleep.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 13,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-74",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Also, make sure your bedroom is dark, quiet, and cool.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 10,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-75",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "A comfortable mattress and pillow can also help improve sleep quality.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 11,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-76",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "Q9.",
      "text": "Why is sleep essential for our health?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 7,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-77",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "Q10.",
      "text": "How many hours of sleep do most adults need per night?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 11,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-78",
      "sectionId": "passage-1",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 1",
      "speaker": "Q11.",
      "text": "What are some of the consequences of lack of sleep?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 10,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-79",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Volunteering is a great way to give back to your community and make a positive difference in the lives of others.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 21,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-80",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It can also have many benefits for you personally.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 9,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-81",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Volunteering can help you develop new skills and gain valuable work experience.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 12,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-82",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "For example, if you volunteer at a hospital, you can learn about healthcare and develop communication and interpersonal skills.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 19,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-83",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "If you volunteer at a non-profit organization, you can learn about fundraising, marketing, and event planning.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 17,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-84",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Volunteering can also help you meet new people and make friends.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 11,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-85",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It allows you to connect with people who share your interests and values.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 13,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-86",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "This can help reduce feelings of isolation and loneliness.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 9,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-87",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "In addition, volunteering can improve your mental health.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 8,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-88",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It can give you a sense of purpose and accomplishment, and it can help reduce stress and anxiety.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 18,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-89",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Studies have shown that people who volunteer regularly are happier and more satisfied with their lives than those who do not.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 21,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-90",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "There are many different ways to volunteer.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 7,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-91",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "You can volunteer at a local school, hospital, animal shelter, or non-profit organization.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 14,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-92",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "You can also volunteer online, by helping with website design, writing, or social media management.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 15,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-93",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "Q12.",
      "text": "What are some of the benefits of volunteering?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 8,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-94",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "Q13.",
      "text": "What can you learn by volunteering at a hospital?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 9,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-95",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "Q14.",
      "text": "How does volunteering improve mental health?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 6,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-96",
      "sectionId": "passage-2",
      "sectionTitle": "PASSAGE 2",
      "speaker": "Q15.",
      "text": "What are some different ways to volunteer?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 7,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-97",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Globalization is the process of increasing interconnectedness and interdependence among countries around the world.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 14,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-98",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It has been driven by advances in technology, transportation, and communication, which have made it easier to trade goods and services, move people and capital, and share ideas and culture.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 30,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-99",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Globalization has many benefits.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 4,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-100",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It has led to increased economic growth, reduced poverty, and improved living standards in many countries.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 16,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-101",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It has also allowed consumers to access a wider variety of goods and services at lower prices.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 17,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-102",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "In addition, globalization has promoted cultural exchange and understanding between different countries and cultures.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 14,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-103",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "However, globalization also has some drawbacks.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 6,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-104",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It has led to increased inequality, both within and between countries.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 11,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-105",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It has also caused job losses in some industries, as companies move their operations to countries with lower labor costs.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 20,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-106",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "In addition, globalization has contributed to environmental degradation, as increased trade and production lead to higher levels of pollution and resource consumption.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 22,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-107",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "To address these challenges, we need to ensure that globalization is more inclusive and sustainable.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 15,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-108",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "This includes implementing policies to reduce inequality, protect workers' rights, and preserve the environment.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 14,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-109",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "We also need to promote international cooperation and dialogue to address global issues, such as climate change and poverty.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 19,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-110",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "Q16.",
      "text": "What is globalization?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 3,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-111",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "Q17.",
      "text": "What are some of the benefits of globalization?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 8,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-112",
      "sectionId": "recording-1",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 1",
      "speaker": "Q18.",
      "text": "What are some of the drawbacks of globalization?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 8,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-113",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Nutrition is an important part of a healthy lifestyle.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 9,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-114",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "The food we eat provides us with the energy and nutrients we need to grow, develop, and function properly.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 19,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-115",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "A balanced diet should include a variety of foods from all the food groups: fruits, vegetables, whole grains, lean proteins, and healthy fats.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 23,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-116",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Fruits and vegetables are rich in vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants, which help protect our bodies from disease.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 17,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-117",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Whole grains provide us with fiber, which helps keep our digestive system healthy.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 13,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-118",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Lean proteins, such as chicken, fish, beans, and nuts, help build and repair our muscles and tissues.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 17,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-119",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Healthy fats, such as olive oil, avocados, and nuts, are important for brain health and hormone production.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 17,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-120",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It is also important to limit our intake of processed foods, sugary drinks, and foods high in saturated and trans fats.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 21,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-121",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "These foods can contribute to weight gain, heart disease, diabetes, and other chronic diseases.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 14,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-122",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "In addition to eating a balanced diet, it is important to stay hydrated by drinking plenty of water.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 18,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-123",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Water is essential for many bodily functions, including digestion, circulation, and temperature regulation.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 13,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-124",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Finally, it is important to eat mindfully.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 7,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-125",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Pay attention to your hunger and fullness cues, and avoid eating when you are stressed or bored.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 17,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-126",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Eating slowly and savoring your food can also help you enjoy your meals more and prevent overeating.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 17,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-127",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "Q19.",
      "text": "What does a balanced diet include?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 6,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-128",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "Q20.",
      "text": "What are fruits and vegetables rich in?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 7,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-129",
      "sectionId": "recording-2",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 2",
      "speaker": "Q21.",
      "text": "What should we limit our intake of?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 7,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-130",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Leadership is the ability to influence and guide others towards a common goal.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 13,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-131",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "It is an important skill that is essential for success in many areas of life, including business, politics, and community organizations.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 21,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-132",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "There are many different leadership styles, and the most effective leaders are able to adapt their style to the situation and the needs of their team.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 26,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-133",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Some common leadership styles include autocratic, democratic, and laissez-faire.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 10,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-134",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Autocratic leaders make decisions without consulting their team members.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 9,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-135",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "This style can be effective in situations where quick decisions need to be made, but it can also lead to low morale and resentment among team members.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 27,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-136",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Democratic leaders involve their team members in the decision-making process.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 11,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-137",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "This style can lead to better decisions and higher morale, but it can also be time-consuming.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 17,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-138",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "Laissez-faire leaders give their team members a lot of freedom and autonomy.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 13,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-139",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "This style can be effective when team members are highly skilled and motivated, but it can also lead to a lack of direction and coordination.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 25,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-140",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "To be an effective leader, you need to have good communication skills, emotional intelligence, and the ability to inspire and motivate others.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 22,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-141",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "",
      "text": "You also need to be able to make tough decisions, take responsibility for your actions, and lead by example.",
      "type": "narration",
      "words": 19,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-142",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "Q22.",
      "text": "What is leadership?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 3,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-143",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "Q23.",
      "text": "What is an autocratic leadership style?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 6,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-144",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "Q24.",
      "text": "What is a democratic leadership style?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 6,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "line-145",
      "sectionId": "recording-3",
      "sectionTitle": "RECORDING 3",
      "speaker": "Q25.",
      "text": "What skills do you need to be an effective leader?",
      "type": "question",
      "words": 10,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 0
    }
  ]
}
